data.description: This lovely home is awaiting its new owner, with so much to offer! Featuring 5 spacious bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms ,  sitting on 5.21 acres along with a refreshing salt water pool w/diving board and slide! This home has been beautifully updated , in the living room you will find gorgeous wooden beams and a stunning brick wood burning fireplace. The kitchen has tons of cabinet space, granite countertops , a wooden island and stainless steel appliances. Also a walk in pantry with plenty of storage and shelving. Just down from the kitchen is a wonderful laundry room with a farm house sink and built in hall tree.  On the main floor you will find the huge owners suite and ensuite with his and hers vanities, as well as 2 more bedrooms and bathrooms. Upstairs you will find a large guest bedroom as well as a bonus room/flex space that could be turned into a 5th bedroom if desired. This home also features 2 new HVACs with air scrubbers, new deep well and new salt water management system for the pool. You've gotta come out and see this one for yourself, porch swinging' coffee sipping, country life at its best!
